---
layout: base.njk
title: "Dubai Node â€” April 2026"
description: "Is AI Going to Take Our Jobs? 25 curated voices. 60 minutes. One question that matters. Apply for your seat at AI TownSquare Dubai."
permalink: /dubai/
extraCss:
  - /css/pages/dubai.css
extraJs:
  - /js/countdown.js
  - /js/form.js
  - /js/pages/dubai-circle.js
  - /js/pages/dubai-radar.js
  - /js/pages/live-feed.js
---

{% from "phase-stepper.njk" import phaseStepper %}

<!-- ============================================
     HERO: Global Readiness Clock
     ============================================ -->
<section class="dubai-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="dubai-hero-content">
      <div class="dubai-hero-eyebrow">Dubai Node &middot; April 2026</div>

      <h1 class="dubai-hero-question">
        <em>Is AI Going to Take Our Jobs?</em>
      </h1>

      <p class="dubai-hero-sub">
        25 curated voices from healthcare, finance, government, and education
        will grapple with one of AI&rsquo;s most pressing questions in a
        structured 60-minute civic dialogue.
      </p>

      <div class="readiness-clock" id="countdown">
        <div class="readiness-clock-label">Global Readiness Clock</div>
        <div class="readiness-clock-units">
          <div class="readiness-clock-unit">
            <span class="readiness-clock-value" id="cd-days">--</span>
            <span class="readiness-clock-name">Days</span>
          </div>
          <div class="readiness-clock-unit">
            <span class="readiness-clock-value" id="cd-hours">--</span>
            <span class="readiness-clock-name">Hours</span>
          </div>
          <div class="readiness-clock-unit">
            <span class="readiness-clock-value" id="cd-min">--</span>
            <span class="readiness-clock-name">Min</span>
          </div>
          <div class="readiness-clock-unit">
            <span class="readiness-clock-value" id="cd-sec">--</span>
            <span class="readiness-clock-name">Sec</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dubai-hero-actions">
        <a href="#register" class="btn btn--primary">
          Apply for 1 of 25 Seats
          <span class="btn-arrow">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================
     CURATED CIRCLE
     ============================================ -->
<section class="curated-circle-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="curated-circle-header reveal">
      <span class="label label--accent">The Room</span>
      <h2 class="curated-circle-title">25 Curated Voices</h2>
      <p class="curated-circle-sub">
        Every seat is intentional. We curate for cross-sector diversity so that
        no single perspective dominates the dialogue.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="curated-circle-ring" id="curatedCircleRing">
      <div class="curated-circle-center">
        <span class="curated-circle-center-num">25</span>
        <span class="curated-circle-center-label">Voices</span>
      </div>
      <!-- Nodes positioned by dubai-circle.js -->
    </div>

    <div class="curated-circle-legend">
      {% set sectors = {
        "Healthcare": "#2B7A78",
        "Finance": "#D4A843",
        "Government": "#3B6FA0",
        "Education": "#E07A5F",
        "Technology": "#3AAFA9",
        "Citizen": "#8896AB"
      } %}
      {% for name, color in sectors %}
      <div class="curated-circle-legend-item">
        <span class="curated-circle-legend-dot" style="background: {{ color }}"></span>
        {{ name }}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================
     MAIN CONTENT: Phase Stepper + Host + Feed
     ============================================ -->
<section style="background: var(--bg); padding: 120px 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="dubai-main-layout">

      <!-- Sidebar: Phase Stepper -->
      {{ phaseStepper(1, 'Dubai') }}

      <!-- Main content column -->
      <div>
        <!-- HOST CARD -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: 80px;">
          <div style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
            <span class="label label--accent reveal">Your Host</span>
          </div>
          <div class="host-card reveal">
            <div class="host-avatar">OV</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="host-name">Olga V.</h3>
              <p class="host-title">Lead Facilitator, AI TownSquare &middot; Protocol Host</p>
              <p class="host-bio">
                Olga brings deep expertise in structured civic dialogue and
                cross-sector facilitation. Her work bridges technology leaders,
                policymakers, and citizens&mdash;ensuring every voice in the room
                shapes the outcome, not just the loudest ones.
              </p>
              <div class="host-credentials">
                <span class="host-credential">Protocol Facilitator</span>
                <span class="host-credential">Civic Dialogue</span>
                <span class="host-credential">Cross-Sector Design</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- LIVE SYNTHESIS FEED (inline) -->
        {% include "live-feed.njk" %}
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================
     SRI RADAR CHART (Hexagonal SVG)
     ============================================ -->
<section class="dubai-sri-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="dubai-sri-header reveal">
      <span class="label label--accent">Societal Readiness Index</span>
      <h2 class="dubai-sri-title">Dubai&rsquo;s Readiness Profile</h2>
      <p class="dubai-sri-sub">
        Six pillars measuring how prepared Dubai is for AI integration.
        Scores are weighted by institutional importance.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="dubai-radar-wrap reveal">
      <svg id="dubaiRadarChart" class="dubai-radar-svg" viewBox="0 0 500 500" aria-label="Hexagonal radar chart showing Dubai SRI scores">
        <!-- Rendered by dubai-radar.js -->
      </svg>
      <div class="dubai-radar-tooltip" id="radarTooltip">
        <div class="dubai-radar-tooltip-title" id="radarTooltipTitle"></div>
        <div id="radarTooltipDesc"></div>
        <div class="dubai-radar-tooltip-source" id="radarTooltipSource">Data Source: AI TownSquare SRI</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================
     REGISTRATION
     ============================================ -->
<section class="register section--dark" id="register">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="register-inner">
      <div class="register-header">
        <span class="label label--highlight reveal">Apply Now</span>
        <h2 class="register-title reveal">
          Claim Your Seat at<br/>
          <span class="register-title-accent">AI TownSquare Dubai</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="register-subtitle reveal">25 seats. Curated for cross-sector diversity. Your background matters.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="register-form-wrap reveal">
        <form id="registerForm" action="https://formspree.io/f/{{ site.formspreeId }}" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Dubai Node Application" />
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">Full Name *</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-input" name="name" required />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">Email Address *</label>
              <input type="email" class="form-input" name="email" required />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">Organization *</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-input" name="organization" required />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">Role / Title *</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-input" name="role" required />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label">I am a... *</label>
            <select class="form-select" name="category" required>
              <option value="">Select your category</option>
              <option value="builder">Builder (tech, AI, product)</option>
              <option value="user">User (business, operations)</option>
              <option value="regulator">Regulator (policy, government)</option>
              <option value="academic">Academic (research, education)</option>
              <option value="healthcare">Healthcare professional</option>
              <option value="finance">Finance &amp; banking</option>
              <option value="citizen">Citizen (general public)</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label">Why does this topic matter to you? *</label>
            <textarea class="form-textarea" name="reason" rows="4" placeholder="1-2 sentences about your perspective on AI and jobs" required></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="form-submit" id="submitBtn">
            Submit Application &rarr;
          </button>
        </form>

        <p class="form-note">
          We curate for diversity across sectors, roles, and perspectives.<br/>
          You&rsquo;ll hear back within 48 hours.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="register-details reveal">
        <div class="register-detail">
          <div class="register-detail-label">Date</div>
          <div class="register-detail-value">April 2026</div>
        </div>
        <div class="register-detail">
          <div class="register-detail-label">Location</div>
          <div class="register-detail-value">Dubai, UAE</div>
        </div>
        <div class="register-detail">
          <div class="register-detail-label">Format</div>
          <div class="register-detail-value">In-Person + Hybrid</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
